Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(248,261)\fs20\fad(650,900)}热风!狂飙!碓冰山道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.86,0:02:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常不妙 我能行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方能行的话 我没可能不行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.48,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着 紧贴内线 抓地过弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干得好 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,障碍物 让出内线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有两下子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是普通的车手呢 紧咬着不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这都做不到 到后面就没有乐趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.16,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟到什么程度呢 我们的实力可不仅止于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真够呛 无法自己驾驭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能被动跟跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就像过山车一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.38,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法作出自己的节奏 所以才觉得可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这里被甩开的话就绝对追不上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不熟悉道路 比想象中更加不利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意力减退的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是撞上山壁就是摔落谷底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是如今轰动一时的秋名86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没那么容易甩开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以为是右转 其实是左转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是碓冰弯道的恐怖之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着右转 很窄哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快 可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎么能被你甩开呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方能转的话 我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.32,0:06:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海那小子 他说对方能转自己应该也能转是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很肯定地说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以置信 非常单纯的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的脑子里到底装了什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但换句话说那是个了不起的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有他那样的技术是想不出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.91,0:06:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说入弯不超出极限还是能控制的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用说当然能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.12,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可对手怎么说也是对道路了如指掌...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然会将速度提至极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海也用同样的速度入弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这一无所知的碓冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.43,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不寒而栗啊 光是想就觉得恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是技术 没有过人的胆识也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.93,0:07:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍有闪失车就会完全报废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像说对手是什么Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80是什么车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被咬住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么? 是我开得不好吗? 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有的事 你状态很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可他紧跟在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别看后视镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会影响节奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面的动向我会好好留心 没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是才开始嘛 要好好享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是最棒的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 交给我吧 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是 请相信搭档哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子和我是碓冰最快的最佳组合哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先行者将后追者甩开就算赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法甩开的话再互换位置 直到决出胜负为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是骤死赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种规则的话 第一轮肯定选先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为能确保拖延到第二轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有一轮可以练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二轮输了也没那么难看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一轮我从后面出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再想清楚 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的比赛 我自己会决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我是不喜欢后面被人跟着才选的后追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到会这么危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生疏的道路上跑 最难的一点...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是决定入弯速度的判断力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,启介输掉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及中里的32被超都是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.37,0:09:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管技术再好也赢不了长期在本地跑的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么要赢秋名86的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能赢 凭这个理论的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算在他的主场秋名山也能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 太小看她们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我下了个危险之极的赌注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入弯前仅有几厘米的路线误差...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或速度误差的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出弯后就会发展成巨大的误差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保险杠擦到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 绝不能被甩开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.50,0:10:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多体验几次心脏极度收缩的瞬间 车手才会成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与众不同的注意力和感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千锤百炼的驾驶技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上最重要的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我亲手炮制完美的悬挂设定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不会输吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样了呢? 已经有结果了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没回来前还不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.91,0:11:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太勉强了 再怎么偏袒也找不到有利条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 池谷前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.26,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前也没有一个条件对拓海有利过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中里的32那像怪物般的车...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庄司那家伙的胶带死亡赛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对拓海来说都是初次经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管如此拓海仍有唯一的优势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是地点在秋名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海五年间每天都不断在跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.15,0:12:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前辈 道路不同 真会有那么大的影响?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑几次的话情况还好点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可拓海完完全全是第一次跑这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 池谷 我有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.04,0:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子助手席上的那个女孩是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你问我 我还想问你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是比赛 还理所当然地坐在旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,详情我也不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只听说好像是童年的至交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.53,0:12:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初学时两人总是一起研究...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并完成了驾驶技术的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.79,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不就像是拉力赛的领航员一样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样一来拓海就更不利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.98,0:13:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 拓海没理由输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果身旁有优秀的领航员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子只需注意驾驶就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弯道前有障碍物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲开后再占回内线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甩不掉 这样的高节奏仍然跟得上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子在绝佳状态居然还被咬住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.75,0:14:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子 马上就到C=121了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一决胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入口开始就尽全力滑过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强行一次性解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这碓冰山道最难的弯道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白 就这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他见识一下从入口一直甩到出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没人用和我同样速度入弯后能成功出弯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子和沙雪今晚不来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.09,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁知道呢 还没见到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想看Sil-80的漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这C=121弯道是最棒的观察点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难度也极高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不能用难来形容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在这儿从入口一直甩到出口的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就称得上是碓冰山道的高手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碓冰的高手 到哪儿都是最强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没胆量一口气拼死入弯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.49,0:15:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度不够 漂移就无法持续到出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次尝试的人全都失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但熟练之后也有人能做到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.65,0:16:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能以全油门不刹车入弯就只有真子的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道她大概练了多久才掌握的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那种程度却没人能模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人从上面下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好响的轮胎尖叫声 要冲过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.96,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真子和沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面还有车 是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在比赛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是86吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有对向车 华丽地冲吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入弯了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以理解 居然以真子同样的速度入弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知死活的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不知道C=121的难度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可不是靠什么狗屎胆量就能成功的弯道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有毅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然能紧贴着真子入弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.29,0:17:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了这种速度就只能凭真本事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.83,0:17:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,C=121中间很宽敞 但出口却极端狭窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看上去路线很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能成功的却只有一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.73,0:18:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第一次跑的道路上 第一轮就能驾驭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那86是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道...难道那家伙就是最近盛传的秋名86?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鸡皮疙瘩都起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超极限速度的四轮漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是Ultra D的难度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.84,0:19:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连熟练了的真子出弯时与最佳路线也差了五厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那家伙却修正至理想线路出了弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,选了个相差悬殊的怪物来做比赛对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,错了 这弯道动作不能那么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就请在入弯前说啊 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.32,0:19:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 别发呆啊 不像平时的你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不明白 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面的86是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是现在的我们能应付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 平时不是很爱逞强吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.26,0:20:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还没输你就想放弃了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话是没错...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.79,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 没想到你那么胆怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能再靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那辆86的厉害不是早就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.91,0:20:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但已经决定这是最后的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们不全力以赴的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切就都结束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道你在害怕什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的沙雪最差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是助手席上的累赘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累赘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是个会破坏功重比的压舱物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.47,0:20:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一握方向盘人就变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说我是压舱物算什么意思啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是身材好 我又不是肥婆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可还是多了四十九公斤的不利因素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是四十七公斤!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到这份上也不能再忍气吞声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.63,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命地冲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.36,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 下个弯道 用几乎撞上内侧岩石的气势切入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不顾后果地追跑到现在已经完全习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我掌握了这条山道的节奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能以自己的节奏来跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的弯道不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不到最后不能泄气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.31,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲刺 冲刺 再冲刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.34,0:22:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想留下悔恨 即使赌上碓冰山道最快的尊严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.50,0:24:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文太先生 和Sil-80的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.45,0:24:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海有胜算吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.40,0:24:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.42,0:24:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这么说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.34,0:24:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是开豆腐店的 不是预言家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.55,0:24:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我煎豆腐饼和炸豆腐块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.90,0:24:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是我精心炮制的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.08,0:24:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下山的话绝不会输给任何车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.67,0:24:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然还要根据车手的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.46,0:24:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬请期待下星期吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.80,0:24:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.75,0:24:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木棉豆腐和绢豆腐我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.11,0:24:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 头文字D 决战!超级漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.16,0:24:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.44,0:24:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别错过

